data.description: New neighborhood new craftsman style looks for this builder. Brick & Board & Batten Vinyl Siding, 1,750 SF+/- plus a 2-car garage, 3 bedrooms, 2 baths on .51 acre lot+/-. The kitchen is the heart of the home surrounded by the dining room & great room w/trey ceilings & a free standing work island with a breakfast bar, all overlooking the back yard with a covered patio.  The kitchen has stainless appliances, undermount sink, backsplash, white cabinets/accent color for the island all with granite countertops & a walk in pantry. Master bedroom is spacious with trey ceilings, an incredible master bath, a walk-in shower, 2 vanities & a large walk in closet.  2 other bedrooms, the guest bathroom has granite counter top vanity & a tub shower combo.  Laundry room is just inside the 2 car garage, easy access to the kitchen.  Luxury vinyl plank throughout, carpet in bedrooms only.  Alabama power, City of Clanton Sewer, Water, Garbage SHOWN BY APPOINTMENT ONLY.
